{"tid":753863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一回頭卻發現自己已面目全非","createTime":"2018-07-24T03:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T05:58:28.000Z","uid":6579,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec61cd762a8b961daf9a78a2983897c7138ce8f","tid":753863,"uid":6579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:12:15.000Z","msg":"有無人一樣<br />\n經歷過情路上跌跌碰碰後<br />\n回頭一望，細數返自己心境既轉變<br />\n先至發現已經變左另一個人<br />\n當初果個對愛情充滿美好憧憬，<br />\n以為初戀可以行到老<br />\n以為1+1=2<br />\n以為忍過就雨過天晴<br />\n以為付出就會有回報既傻豬<br />\n<br />\n到依家心態扭曲得不成人形<br />\n著住名為player食家既盔甲<br />\n「有酒今朝醉」「活在當下」「食左先算」<br />\n歸根究底只係怕盔甲背後果個軟弱無能既自己再受傷害<br />\n<br />\n從無求 到渴求 直到渴求整個宇宙<br />\n來到最後卻只想得救"},{"pid":"5d10feef7c8dd6b4eb180a1c61a8514ae8ba917a","tid":753863,"uid":6579,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:14:55.000Z","msg":"心知自己傷過好多人<br />\n深知自己十惡不赦<br />\n亦深信報應係呢刻已經發生緊<br />\n他朝君體"},{"pid":"61a02dc4c34fd0e285e2e57231589f180660752a","tid":753863,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:17:02.000Z","msg":"Wfc"},{"pid":"1ea451b0082c7cf9d0c6bb53fe67f4311203e8bd","tid":753863,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"再強捍都敵不過洋腸.jpg"},{"pid":"3517b608a7539d2988a698bf880928947feaa008","tid":753863,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/112540_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F112540_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=674b69f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bffff1c876615b1698bace45a9308b77b34a511","tid":753863,"uid":186708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"如能忘掉渴望 歲月長 衣裳薄"},{"pid":"1d2848174c3b83ce2cbc460c545910d29cc5a544","tid":753863,"uid":154054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"c